A plant known as the Deadly Nightshade is the main player. Timer that allows 1 minute of game play, and each enemy that is not destroyed
drains the player of energy.
X key enables photosynthetic energy boost. that boost energy level.
[Arrow Keys] to move player
[SPACE] to release poison bullets.


Level 1
In a cave scene, the plant only has a single enemy. Bacteria moves downwards. Two spawn for every timeout.

Level 2
In a tropical jungle scene, the plant has two enemies for each timeout. One Bacteria and one Insect.

Level3 3
In a dark swamp, the plant has three enemies: Enemy, Insect, and Virus that spawns at each timeout. 
The virus spawns especially fast as the spawn functions connects a timer to a specific Viral spawn function.
